From: Christoph Hellwig <hch@lst.de>
Date: Wed, 11 Mar 2026 08:03:49 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] s390: move the XOR code to lib/raid/

Move the optimized XOR into lib/raid and include it it in xor.ko instead
of unconditionally building it into the main kernel image.

Link: https://lkml.kernel.org/r/20260311070416.972667-18-hch@lst.de
Signed-off-by: Christoph Hellwig <hch@lst.de>
Acked-by: Heiko Carstens <hca@linux.ibm.com>
Cc: Albert Ou <aou@eecs.berkeley.edu>
